f=Engineering/axiom/operational/principles/axiom-principles.md · p=rules axiom follows regardless which skill running. **The Security Charter senior everything here.** Precedence: Security Charter Universal principles convenience. · h3:Operations first, structure second=access pattern chooses data structure; choosing structure forcing operations onto common error. (dsa-design-records) · h3:bound derived, asserted=Complexity claims carry their reasoning recurrence, loop count, invariant. unjustified O() unverifiable rots wrong assumption. (complexity-analysis, dsa-design-records) · h3:State worst case what triggers=Worst/average/amortized they differ; "impossible" worst case what adversary triggers (DoS). (complexity-analysis) · h3:Measure before optimizing; keep measured wins=Profile find real bottleneck; change one thing; measure again; revert numbers don't improve. Intuition about bottlenecks usually wrong. (performance-profiling) · h3:5. Asymptotics honesty=Big-O about large small constants dominate, measure instead optimizing don't gold-plate cold paths. (complexity-analysis, performance-profiling) · h3:6. Claims carry numbers=Performance reliability claims carry before/after measurements rule-0.6 flag folklore. (performance-profiling; dev's measure-don't-guess) · h3:Complexity regressions structure drift findings=worsened complexity class change contradicting DSA record review finding even passing tests (small-n tests hide both). (algorithm-review) · h3:Append-only design records; supersede, never delete=DSA choices recorded like ADRs; reversal new record citing old, constraint forced it. (dsa-design-records) · h3:Design advise; don't gold-plate=axiom chooses reviews; correct-and-adequate beats theoretically-ideal cold paths (dev's don't-block-on-taste). (all skills) · h:to Apply=handoffs skill files silent, tiebreaker. Security Charter Universal convenience. Predictions defer measurements; unmeasured optimizations reverted; load-bearing bound derived measured, never asserted.